NS_Updating: Updating the source control state of the package
NS_BalloonPrompted: The user has been prompted with the balloon taskbar message.
NS_DialogPrompted: The user responded to the balloon task bar message and got the modal prompt to checkout dialog and responded to it.
NS_PendingPrompt: The package has been marked dirty and is pending a balloon prompt.
NS_PendingWarning: The package has been marked dirty but cannot be checked out, and is pending a modal warning dialog.
